---
import Section from '../Section.astro';
import Container from '../Container.astro';
import Eyebrow from '../Eyebrow.astro';
import Stat from '../Stat.astro';

const stats = [
  { value: '23 yrs', label: 'Regional consulting heritage via e-CENS' },
  { value: '7', label: 'MEA offices across UAE, KSA, Egypt and beyond' },
  { value: '4', label: 'Global Google Marketing Platform Partners — e-CENS is one' },
  { value: '80,000+', label: 'Engineers in the FPT global delivery network' },
];
---

<Section tone="dark">
  <Container>
    <div class="grid gap-16 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(0,1fr)] lg:gap-24">
      <div>
        <Eyebrow>The 2026–2027 Window</Eyebrow>
        <h2 class="mt-4 text-display-lg">
          The next 18 months will define the next decade of MEA digital transformation.
        </h2>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-platinum/85">
        <p class="text-lead">
          Government, BFSI, and Retail leaders across the UAE, KSA, and Egypt are entering
          the most concentrated procurement window in the region's history. Vision 2030,
          the UAE's We the UAE 2031 agenda, and Egypt's Vision 2030 are converging into a
          single inflection point — and the consultancies that win will be the ones that
          combine in-country accountability with proven global delivery muscle.
        </p>
        <p>
          Emerge Digital was built for exactly this moment. We are the Dubai Mainland prime
          that owns your contract, structures your program, and stands accountable in your
          jurisdiction — while our JV partners e-CENS and FPT Corporation bring 23 years of
          regional CX, data, and analytics leadership and 80,000+ engineers of global
          delivery capacity behind every engagement.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-12 border-t border-white/8 pt-12 md:grid-cols-4">
      {stats.map((s) => <Stat value={s.value} label={s.label} />)}
    </div>
  </Container>
</Section>
